360	```
361	
362	### 4. 测试用例
363	
364	```java
365	// 测试 Unsafe 边界检查
366	@Test(expected = IllegalArgumentException.class)
367	public void testCannotWriteToKlassField() {
368	    Object obj = new Object();
369	    Unsafe unsafe = getUnsafe();
370	    
371	    // 应该抛出异常
